(NULL,'UpGrad','49074','Anindya','Abhishek Reddy','Re: Re:[## 1726135 ##] Re: Your Bulk Update Request - Leads Bulk Update - Partial Success  this was not an Import activity but a BULK UPDATE on leads to apply a unique zip. I cannot even download the lead dump as the bulk update was partial success. Also, I download the partial BULK UPDATE SUCCESS dump - exports will fail after a wait time of 20-30 Mins.   Export Failing Issue example below -    Either bulk updates are failing or completing with a Partial Success. Or the Lead dump exports are failing - I tried 2 times one with selected fields and the other one with all fields. The export was stuck in progress for 20 minutes and then showcased the Failure message.   It is an recurring issue which is hampering daily Operations. Prior to this I have highlighted the same issue 3 times.','P1','Support',1882448,NULL,'Integration Failures','Data sync issues','2026-03-17','20/04/2026','Resolved','support to check with product team'),
(NULL,'Rank Guru','72070','Anindya','Abhishek Reddy','RE: [#1879520] Infinity Learn (B2B) - 72070 || SIERA Report creation Please help to raise a dev ticket to track the below request to create a SIERA report. The details of the report are available in this RL ticket: https://onboarding.leadsquared.com/projects/275417/plan#task_drawer=275417.33020187&task_drawer_tab=conversations','P1','Support',1879520,1881665,'Reports & Dashboards','Reports & Dashboards related','2026-03-09',NULL,'Resolved','SIERA team to help build the report.'),
(NULL,'Practo','33121','Anindya','Abhishek Reddy','RE: [#1879299] RE: Re:[## 1714411 ##] Need to Retrieve Lead Documents The field which contains the document in part of a custom field set for a lead. The Lead Details API returns the filename instead of its URL. For your reference, the field is mx_CustomObject_13 inside mx_Discharge_To_Complete.','P2','PS',1879299,NULL,'PS','Change Request','2026-03-12',NULL,'Resolved','Cx to share details of the number of leads where this data needs to be exported. 20-Apr - Cx shared info. PS to check and help with steps to retrieve details. 1-May - Followed up with PS.'),
